information: Femago is one of the main auctions in Almería, Spain. It is in El Ejido and its origins go back to the thirties. Our goal from the very start was to become one of the biggest auction halls in Almería. Almost 80 years at the service of Almeria’s farmers. Decades of work as intermediaries between the farmer and the buyer, providing value and solutions to both. The buyer benefits from a comprehensive product offering, permanent quality control, handling, loading and unloading, traceability and other services.Femago exports different vegetables and fruits. Femago works the European market intensively with buyers from Spain itself, Germany, France, the United Kingdom, Eastern Europe, Italy, the Netherlands and Belgium...We are so interested in building business relationships.
